text: Marina Katić (born 1 October 1983) is a Croatian national volleyball player. She played at the 2009 Women's European Volleyball Championship, 2010 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship, and 2015 FIVB World Grand Prix. She played for Igtisadchi Baku, MKS Dąbrowa Górnicza, and Imoco Conegliano. == References == Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Croatian volleyball players
